# Olist Brazilian E-Commerce — Data Analysis Project

End-to-end data analysis project using the Olist e-commerce dataset.
Pipeline: PostgreSQL → Python (ETL) → Tableau.

## Project Status
🚧 In progress · Phase 1 of 6

## Tech Stack
- **Database:** PostgreSQL 17
- **Languages:** SQL, Python (Pandas, SQLAlchemy)
- **Visualization:** Tableau
- **Version control:** Git

## Repository Structure

    01-loading/    -- Database schema and data loading
    02-queries/    -- Analytical SQL queries

## Dataset
[Olist Brazilian E-Commerce Public Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/olistbr/brazilian-ecommerce)
9 relational tables · ~100k orders · 2016–2018

